    "asOf": "2021-04-21",
    "date": "2021-11-23T20:11:47Z",
    "text": "United States-Mexico Tourism Improvement Act of 2021\n\nThis bill directs the Department of State to develop and report to Congress a strategy to improve bilateral tourism between the United States and Mexico and third-party tourism to the two countries. The strategy shall involve dialogue and cooperation between the two governments, and it shall prioritize sectors including hospitality, retail, and cultural education."
